result.name: Chat Point

reviews.text: Taiwanese food with a wide range of drinks to choose like bubble milk tea, green milk tea, iced drinks. Food are simple with snacks served mostly. Toasts are the best food could be ordered. The restaurant is quite small with limited seating.

Reasonable price at around 50-60hkd for a meal. Sells Taiwanese food, the food is ok for the price range and comes with extensive bubble tea selection (ofc it's the powdered bubble tea kind with sugar syrup, not real tea but not expecting anything fancy for the price). 

Seating is cramped due to it being a super small shop and it gets really busy during lunch hours as it's usually filled with high school students. Better to go at other times or non school days to avoid the students.
Small restaurant serving Taiwanese cuisine at reasonable prices. Seating for around 20 people max. Good food & can be bought to take-out.
Small resto... full of flavors, amazing quick service, great food and resonably priced. A must try in Tai Po, Hongkong.
Good food

result.formatted_address: 1 On Chee Road, Treasure Garden 7B, Tai Po, 香港
result.name: 茶點

reviews.text:
鹽焗手撕雞米線+秘製麻辣油，勁正！
加埋嘢飲都係$46咋，算底！
只可惜地方細了一點！
但在非繁忙時間，不算擠逼，看著店舖內的佈置，聽著不吵耳的流行曲(國語歌多)，感覺優閒！舒服！寫意！有種去如了台灣的感覺！😊
小地方，價廉☕，要求不高也是不錯聚腳之處，OK啦，
茶㸃的豆腐肉燥鹵水蛋飯&香芋珍珠奶茶😍😋
消委會與食物安全中心合作檢測市面8款共127個台式飲品樣本，此店芒果綠茶每杯糖含量達30克，等如6粒方糖。
鷄絲肉燥飯實在太好吃👍👍花枝丸米線👍😋😋

result.formatted_address: 1 On Chee Rd, Tai Po, Hong Kong
result.name: Treasure Garden

reviews.text: Good

這裡旺中帶靜，出入方便，出市區巴士路線四通八達，又可轉乘港鐵。
樓下己變作食街，食店林林總總，各式其式。附近又有公園、球場、天后廟、室內運動場、街市等等。
四週的綠化也做得不錯，所以在這裡都覺得好服 !
轉眼間已好多年，不管你喜不喜歡，大埔區隨着大埔中心一帶廣範發展，那邊已成為旺區，所以樓價一直不平，買得起就住，買唔起就冇得住，如此簡單，話冇乜好行或者廁所汚糟都是廢話，講哩啲毫無意思！
静中带旺，出入交通方便，管理良好！
亂、漏、味道唔得、樓面招呼唔專業！
